        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 4. Pedrocortesella spp. Leg I structures. A--C: Pedrocortesella anica n.sp. A, genu, tibia and tarsus, antiaxial; B, detail tarsus, distal; C, tibia (distal) and tarsus, dorsal. D,E: Pedrocortesella callitarsus n.sp. D, genu, tibia and tarsus, antiaxial; E, tarsal cluster, detail. Scale bars: A,D 50 fJm; B,C,E = 10 fJm. A-C = Canberra; D,E = Mount Gingera." ;
